{"tid":1640006,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"火之魔法師，入門版","createTime":"2019-10-08T22:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T22:25:47.000Z","uid":236687,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7cfa282c6341ed5550ebc6e1c6ad44f12764d701","tid":1640006,"uid":236687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:10:56.000Z","msg":"相信大家細個都曾經想學好似電視入面d動漫主角咁，識得用各種魔法<br />\n<br />\n而現實生活中，火之魔法師對普通人來講可能係一個好難觸摸嘅境界，加上技術不足又驚燒錯隔離，令好多人選擇放棄自細嘅夢想<br />\n<br />\n但係！其實只要有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">心</span></strong>！人人都可以係魔法師！<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">人人都可以使出火之滅龍魔法！人人都可以係納茲！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n只要有<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>止汗劑/殺蟲劑</strong></span>一支，<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">火機</span></strong>一個。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Boom&iexcl;&iexcl;&iexcl;</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n恭喜你！已經成為一名見習火之魔法師<br />\n<br />\n平時出街打完波行到成身汗！有支止汗劑旁身係十分正常合理嘅事！周圍都有得賣止汗劑同火機。即係話！只要有心！人人都可以係魔法師！<br />\n<br />\n雖然入門火魔法師只能學習入門版嘅火焰魔法。遠攻能力相當之差。<br />\n<br />\n但係！<strong>但係！</strong>。近距離自保能力相當出色！就算火機無油，幫對面衝緊過來個d人對眼止下汗，噴濛佢地嘅護目鏡，都起到一定嘅清新作用<br />\n<br />\n只要簡單工具就可以滿足大家嘅童年幻想！<br />\n<br />\n不過大家係成為魔法師之後記得留意周圍嘅人<br />\n<br />\n利申：我就夠鐘食藥，9up嘅野，你地有腦識諗架嘛！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/N-4WoSWlmFc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FN-4WoSWlmFc&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ56X7PLg0GRX82CuX%2BG2FI0%3D&h=b7031b1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/N-4WoSWlmFc</a><br />\n隨post附上好多年前嘅火之魔法師"},{"pid":"218df20068aa25c9226884cb94d9d834ff366025","tid":1640006,"uid":236687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:15:23.000Z","msg":"自推10次以表對魔法師偉大夢想嘅渴望"},{"pid":"f53d5809a72b6a847019544a25bad07cd67fde9c","tid":1640006,"uid":236687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:15:33.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"508c1880bbc7fc4f9ac76614e0db245507e61c61","tid":1640006,"uid":236687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:15:43.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"83acebeb0500510cf528a9c09e3bd151e78003ad","tid":1640006,"uid":236687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:15:53.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"2904b07e82f060b3966cf47982fe9e14e352e45e","tid":1640006,"uid":236687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:16:03.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"3df56707fff217d81b1f1c5f54bc3460ad5675a0","tid":1640006,"uid":236687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:16:13.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"7ea3c1a32502a7193abeeed3c73075128f17ba11","tid":1640006,"uid":236687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:16:23.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"a0c4906f9242217b0525dc4e05aabebd923d2514","tid":1640006,"uid":236687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:16:33.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"7f5118770dcb28d7b2bdee83d10c698c968c939a","tid":1640006,"uid":236687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:16:43.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"5119f9d7bc1f7814e17e5e3ab8c334d20be2b592","tid":1640006,"uid":236687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:16:53.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"1c74b2e108509ee9f70034bba1663df8dcac710e","tid":1640006,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:18:31.000Z","msg":"打機一問<br />\n入門級但直接放落狗到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b23c353e269c82c0c84958458060c1666e3675b","tid":1640006,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:18:44.000Z","msg":"「鞭屍時間」休息撚全部同我收皮！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639206\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639206</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"afa0d8bf674bdbbc89687427f3e4e29b45a07004","tid":1640006,"uid":236687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c74b2e108509ee9f70034bba1663d